args:
The prince goes undercover to investigate with
the apostles. Madame rewrites people's
memories right before their eyes. The apostles
are confident that a sealing stone is involved,
but when Pinon gives Madame a pat-down,
she discovers nothing of the sort on her person.
Gooooood morning, everyone! I'd like to\nintroduce a friendly new face to you!
Nice to meet you all.\nMy name's {player_name}.
Pinon invited him here. Let's all give her\na big round of applause for making our\nhome a little bit more heavenly!
Only we can keep this community thriving!\nNow, everybody, where's our happy place?
Hrah! Hngah! The soil's pretty hard-packed.
Leave that to me, then.\nAnd-a ONE! *WHAM*
Whoa. The soil'll be tilled in no time flat.\nYou're something else, Ryszarda.

I'm just blessed with raw strength, that's
all. I'm a total coward, so compared to
everyone else, I'm not quite so reliable
or level-headed...
Hoed to perfection, thanks to Ryszarda.\nHow are things with you two?

We went to keep watch, but the village is
as peaceful as can be. So much so that I
question the necessity of a neighborhood
watch in the first place.
Faris should be back any minute from\ngathering medicinal herbs. Then we\ncan all take a nice lunch break together.
Right. It'll be a good opportunity for us\nto share the intel we've gathered, too.
Goodness, my Little Pi! Let's get those\ncrumbs cleaned off your mouth. Hold still.
Hey, I know how to use a napkin, okay?\nI'm not a child anymore.
Ha ha! What a sweet relationship you\ntwo seem to have.
Gabriel's motherly tendencies are\nwell-known among the apostles.
*sigh* How long are we going to do this?\nWeren't we going to share intelligence?
That's right. Now, from what I've gathered,\nMadame doesn't generally make public\nappearances.

The only exception is during a nighttime
gathering of some sort. People petition her
for counsel, and she imparts them with
memories that best assuage their worries.
I see. As for me, I went to check on the\nothers from the Halidom under the\npretense of gathering herbs.
Not just any spring water. It's one of the\ningredients for making sanctified water.
You need only dissolve the mana of\na special mineral into it to create\nthe sanctified water that we apostles use.
I'd like you to do exactly that to make\nus a cleansing fount so we can refill\nour supply.
We do still have a bit on hand, mind you.

Once we confirm that the rewritten
memories are being caused by a sealing
stone, we'll purge the miasma corrupting
the villagers with said sanctified water.
All I did in the meantime was till the\nfields. I don't really have any intel. Sorry...
That's fine. We need to blend into the\nvillage anyway to keep the proverbial\nwool pulled over the villagers' eyes.

Prior to our infiltration, the Church
dispatched Templars here for an
investigation, but all of them have
disappeared.
Once night falls, the gathering will begin.\nThen we can assess Madame's power for\nourselves.
This is quite the venue.\nIt's practically a palace.
Down in front, girl!\nYou're in my way. I can't see!
Oh, pardon me!\nI'll move right now!
You should have just done that to begin\nwith, you bonehead.
Easy, pal. She did as you asked.\nYou could stand to be a little nicer.
Do you want to dare say that again?!\nWhat's it to you?!
That's enough. I'm with the neighborhood\nwatch, and if you keep this up, I'm going\nto have to step in.
I'm sorry, Faris. You too, Pinon...

If I've told you once, I've told
you a thousand times, Ryszarda.
Stop apologizing when you haven't
done anything wrong.
Madame is here! MADAME IS HERE!

In a world of manifold sorrows...
To you who are beset by these tribulations,
Madame will be your salvation.
Now, where is our happy place, everyone?
And now, first of the lost seeking succor,\nSTEP FORTH!
Well, I desire a partner, but I'm at a loss\nfor how to go about meeting someone.

If you were to possess memories of lovers
past, then you would naturally know
just how to do so. And as such...
Abrakazam!

I have wiped clean your memories of
bachelorhood, and imbued you with the
experience of a seasoned romantic. Do you
think you can find yourself a partner now?
Does a dragon roar in the woods? I've\ndated more than fifty people in my time!\nAnd now I'm ready to make it a HUNDRED!

I have lived a long life, and so I have seen
the ugly side of humanity time and again.
I wish I could forget all of that and be born
as a different creature.
I know those feelings well. And so, hocus\npocus ally-kazoo, hieeeah!
Gone are your memories of your human\nexistence. Now, you have been a chicken\nsince birth.
What the...? Is she really rewriting\nthese people's memories?

The change I am seeing does seem
to rule out any other explanation.
More pertinent still is the power
that Madame is using!
Yeah. It's miasma. No doubt about it\nMadame is using a sealing stone.

From time to time, I like to call upon one
of you, rather than the other way around.
And I am reminded that we have new
friends among us today.
Yes we do! Come on up,\n{player_name}!
My, what a handsome gentleman. Tell me\nyoung man: what woes tug at your heart?

If you find yourself tongue tied, perhaps I
might venture a guess. Your father has
passed, and your sister has been taken
from you. Am I on the mark, traitor prince?
How do you know that name?!

I wouldn't think people in this part of the
continentespecially in a tiny, secluded
mountain villagewould know about my
circumstances.

You fight to buoy your own spirits.
But have you never once thought that it
might be nice to forget your sordid life,
and to live in comfort?

I can expunge those painful memories
from your mind. This is, after all, a
paradise, young mana place where
comfort awaits you at every turn.
I...still dream about those things even\nnow, you know. About losing my father.\nAbout watching my sister be taken captive.
But I could never, ever let go of those\nmemories. They're a reality that I\nhave to face with unclouded eyes.
Then what did you even come here for?\nTo make fools out of us? HM? Then get\nthe hell out. Get out. Get ooout. Get OUT!
GET OUT! GET OUT!\nGEEET OUT! GEEET OUT!
Oh no, they're turning on us!\nWhat do we do?!

Hey, Madame. Don't you get why
he's hesitating? Is it really smart to let
someone muck around with your memories
using some weird, unknown power?
Why, whatever do you mean by that?
There are rumors. Rumors of a magical\ntool that robs people of their memories\nand has an adverse effect on them.
Could you be suggesting that Madame's\npower comes from such an object?
I'm saying it's possible. So long as the\nsource of her power remains a mystery,\nit's only logical to distrust it.

A wise assessment, but you may rest easy.
My power was granted to me from on high.
If it pleases you, you may search me.
I assure you you'll find no such object.

(Faris sure is a smooth operator,
creating an opening for us to search
Madame directly. And if this does lead
to us finding a sealing stone...)
I'll pat her down myself, then.\nMadame, if you please.
What?! That's impossible!\nAre you sure you were thorough?
I checked her from head to toe.\nShe's clean. I guarantee it.

And so you have proven my power to be
genuine. From this point on, I shall wield
my heavenly powers to grant you salvation.
Now then, where is our happy place?
